  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "For example, Diouf et al. (2023) used LDA enhanced with CoARTEX (Corpus Augmented by a Term Rewarding Algorithm from an Indexation Technique) to extract topics from the verbal autopsy database to understand causes of death.",
    "Luo and Rumshisky (2016) used labeled-LDA to enhance post intensive care unit patient's mortality prediction.",
    "Furthermore, prior studies used LDA to identify procedural themes (Agarwal et al. 2023) and frailty-related topics (Cheng et al. 2017; Shao et al. 2016) in clinical notes of heart failure patients.",
    "Derton et al. (2023) used variational autoencoder topic model to understand drivers of cancer disparities from 230,325 clinical notes of 5,285 patients treated with radiotherapy from 2007 to 2019.",
    "Moreover, TM has been used to mine online medical records of depression (Pan et al. 2023) & cancer patients record (Chiudinelli et al. 2020; Kondratieff et al. 2022; Yin et al. 2019) to monitor treatment patterns."
  ],
